title: V04 — Portable Objects
story: familyzoo
author: Sharpee Tutorial
description: Verify taking, dropping, and inventory with portable items

---

# V4 teaches: portable items, take, drop, inventory

# Start at entrance — zoo map should be here
> look
[OK: contains "Zoo Entrance"]

# Take the map
> take map
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Check inventory
> inventory
[OK: contains "zoo map"]

# Carry map to another room
> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]

# Take the penny
> take penny
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Inventory should show both
> inventory
[OK: contains "zoo map"]
[OK: contains "souvenir penny"]

# Drop the map in this room
> drop map
[OK: contains "Dropped"]

# Map should appear in room now
> look
[OK: contains "zoo map"]

# Go to Petting Zoo and take the feed
> east
[OK: contains "Petting Zoo"]

> take feed
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> inventory
[OK: contains "souvenir penny"]
[OK: contains "bag of animal feed"]

# Scenery is still not takeable
> take goats
[OK: contains "fixed in place"]
